<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Install Quiz Launcher</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #f4efe4;
      --ink: #1b1f16;
      --muted: #5d6555;
      --accent: #cb5f33;
      --panel: rgba(255, 251, 241, 0.82);
      --border: rgba(27, 31, 22, 0.12);
      --font-sans: "Avenir Next", "Gill Sans", "Helvetica Neue", sans-serif;
      --font-mono: "IBM Plex Mono", "Menlo", "Consolas", monospace;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(203, 95, 51, 0.18), transparent 30%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #f8f3e7 0%, #ece3d1 100%);
      color: var(--ink);
      font-family: var(--font-sans);
    }

    main {
      width: min(920px, calc(100% - 32px));
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 48px 0 64px;
    }

    .panel {
      padding: 28px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 24px;
      background: var(--panel);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    }

    .eyebrow {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      color: var(--accent);
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem);
      line-height: 0.95;
    }

    p {
      max-width: 62ch;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 14px;
      margin: 24px 0;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 14px 20px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .button-primary {
      background: var(--accent);
      color: white;
    }

    .button-secondary {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      color: var(--ink);
    }

    code, ol {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
    }

    ol {
      padding-left: 18px;
      color: var(--ink);
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .footnote {
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main>
    <section class="panel">
      <p class="eyebrow">quiz.ktf.ninja/install</p>
      <h1>Install The Quiz Launcher</h1>
      <p>The launcher polls <code>__QUIZ_BASE_URL__/status</code>. After a successful response and a short delay, macOS opens <code>__QUIZ_BASE_URL__</code> in the default browser.</p>

      <div class="actions">
        <a class="button button-primary" href="/downloads/QuizLauncherInstaller-macos.zip">Download macOS Installer</a>
        <a class="button button-secondary" href="/">Open Browser Quiz</a>
      </div>

      <ol>
        <li>Download <code>QuizLauncherInstaller-macos.zip</code>.</li>
        <li>Extract the archive and open <code>Quiz Launcher Installer.app</code>.</li>
        <li>If Gatekeeper blocks the app, use Right Click &gt; Open or allow it from Privacy &amp; Security.</li>
        <li>Log out and back in once to make the LaunchAgent evidence easy to capture.</li>
      </ol>

      <p class="footnote">For the acquisition walkthrough, point DNS or a host override for <code>quiz.ktf.ninja</code> at <code>46.225.142.217</code> so the recovered artifacts contain the intended URL instead of a raw IP.</p>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
